title: Gelish .5 Base & Top Coat Gel SET Harmony Nail Salon UV Manicure Polish Soak Off
description:
This wonderful set of Base and Top Coat gel provides the basics for any style of manicure or pedicure.

Gelish Foundation Base Gel creates the adhesive bond between the nail plate and gel products. This product secures adhesion while not damaging the natural nail plate. Foundation will work with Hand & Nail Harmony Gelish products as a base for Soak Off Gel Polish. Gelish Foudation cures in 10 seconds in a LED Light or 30 seconds in an UV Light.

Gelish Top It Off Gel is a sealer top gel designed to create the ultimate finish with your Gelish Soak Off Polish. It creates a high shine that will not dull, chip or peel. Top It Off is a soak off product that can quickly be removed with Soak Off Gel Remover. This coat cures in 30 seconds in a LED Light or 2 minutes in a UV Light.
